ity","Sperm morphology","Total sperm number","Sperm vitality","Sperm agglutination"],"correctOptions":[4],"correctResponses":null,"explanation":"\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESperm agglutination\u003C/strong\u003E evaluates whether sperm cells stick together in specific patterns (head-to-head, tail-to-tail, or mixed). Significant agglutination often indicates the presence of antisperm antibodies, which can impair fertility.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis observation is distinct from \u003Cstrong\u003Esperm motility\u003C/strong\u003E (the ability of sperm to swim properly), \u003Cstrong\u003Esperm morphology\u003C/strong\u003E (the shape and structure of individual sperm), \u003Cstrong\u003Etotal sperm number\u003C/strong\u003E (the count of sperm cells), and \u003Cstrong\u003Esperm vitality\u003C/strong\u003E (whether sperm cells are alive or dead).\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EA complete semen analysis typically includes:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EVolume (1.5-5.0 mL)\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESperm concentration (\u226515 million/mL)\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETotal motility (\u226540%)\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENormal morphology (\u22654%)\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EVitality (\u226558% live)\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EpH (7.2-8.0)\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E","optionExplanations":["","","","",""],"learningPoints":["Sperm agglutination refers to sperm sticking together in clusters, which can indicate the presence of antisperm antibodies.","Normal semen analysis includes assessment of volume, concentration, motility, morphology, and vitality as key parameters."],"references":["Vasan SS. Semen analysis and sperm function tests: How much to test? Indian J Urol. 2011 Jan;27(1):41-8. doi: 10.4103/0970-1591.78424. PMID: 21716889; PMCID: PMC3114587.","Jequier AM. Semen analysis: a new manual and its application to the understanding of semen and its pathology. Asian J Androl. 2010 Jan;12(1):11-3. doi: 10.1038/aja.2009.12. PMID: 20111075; PMCID: PMC3739678.","Chiamchanya C, Kaewnoonual N, Visutakul P, Manochantr S, Chaiya J. Comparative study of the effects of three semen preparation media on semen analysis, DNA damage and protamine deficiency, and the correlation between DNA integrity and sperm parameters. Asian J Androl. 2010 Mar;12(2):271-7. doi: 10.1038/aja.2009.60. Epub 2009 Dec 14. PMID: 20010846; PMCID: PMC3739082.","Sunder M, Leslie SW. Semen Analysis. [Updated 2022 Oct 24]. In: StatPearls [Internet]. Treasure Island (FL): StatPearls Publishing; 2024 Jan-. Available from: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK564369/"]},"relationships":{"itemRevision":{"data":{"type":"itemRevisions","id":"57062"}},"question":{"data":{"type":"questions","id":"15797"}},"stemMedia":{"data":[]},"explanationMedia":{"data":[]}}},{"type":"itemRevisions","id":"57062","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/itemRevisions/57062"},"attributes":{"createdAt":"2024-12-19T14:43:21+10:30","updatedAt":"2025-01-04T08:42:34+10:30"},"relationships":{"item":{"data":{"type":"items","id":"8488"}},"content":{"data":{"type":"questionRevisions","id":"71566"}}},"meta":{"canDelete":false}},{"type":"tags","id":"67","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/tags/67"},"attributes":{"emoji":"","name":"Basic Science","synonyms":null,"description":null,"position":null,"createdAt":null,"updatedAt":null},"relationships":{"group":{"data":{"type":"tagGroups","id":"5"}},"heading":{"data":null}},"meta":{"itemCount":0}},{"type":"tags","id":"71","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/tags/71"},"attributes":{"emoji":"","name":"Junior","synonyms":null,"description":"Suitable for a junior, pre-clinical medical student","position":0,"createdAt":null,"updatedAt":null},"relationships":{"group":{"data":{"type":"tagGroups","id":"6"}},"heading":{"data":null}},"meta":{"itemCount":0}},{"type":"tags",